data.text:
Hiya!

What does oui oui oulala! mean? I asked a guy (who's French) that I've just begun to see if he was free to get together this weekend and that's what he responded with. I know oui means yes, but the addition of oulala, I'm assuming that's a good thing? But what exactly does that mean in reference to my question? Does that mean he's excited? I would hope so

Hello SheShe81 and welcome to this forum!

This sounds to be a very good news for him as if he didn't expect such a pleasant question from you.
